Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "If Kamala Harris gets 4 more years, instead of a Golden Age, America will be condemned to a fate of decline, desperation, and despair. Your family finances will be permanently destroyed, your borders will be gone forever, tens of millions more illegal aliens will invade our cities and towns, Medicare and Social Security will buckle and collapse."
